 Our Products 
We carry a full selection of:  Fasteners • Tools • Fittings • Hose • Safety Products • Abrasives • Cutting Tools • Chemicals • Electrical • Automotive Fasteners More Info 

 

 
 
 
 Updating Website 
Our website is a work in progress and being updated with new information daily. We currently do not sell our products online, however if you give us a call we would be more than happy to help you place an order over the phone. More Info 

 

 
 
 
 Contact Us 
Address: 1200 W Flint St., Lake Elsinore, CA  Phone: (951) 674-1160 More Info 

About UsAmerican Material Company is a family owned industrial hardware warehouse located in Lake Elsinore, CA. We carry an extensive range of fasteners, fittings, abrasives, tools, chemicals and so much more. We have been serving our customers both locally and throughout southern California since 1996. Our warehouse is open to municipalities, commercial and industrial businesses, homeowners, hobbyists and off-road enthusiasts.
Our staff has over 70 combined years of service in the industrial supply industry. Our experience allows us to work fully within our customers purchasing guidelines, meeting their requirements for accurate, on-time deliveries and competitive pricing.
Warehouse HoursMonday - Friday  8:00AM to 5:00PM
Saturday & Sunday  Closed
We are open to the public!
